*Ujutro* se budim rano da bih stigao na posao. (I wake up early in the morning to be able to make it to work.)

Kada *ujutro* otvorim oči, osjećam se odmorno. (When I open my eyes in the morning, I feel refreshed.)

*Ujutru* se uvijek udobno i ugodno osjećam. (I always feel comfortable and pleasant in the morning.)

Često *ujutro* šetam po parku. (I often take a walk in the park in the morning.)

Kad se *ujutro* probudim, najprije pijem kafu. (When I wake up in the morning, I first have some coffee.)